In the INTEREST OF T.S., Minor Child, S.G., Mother, Petitioner-Appellant, T.A.S., Father, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-1333 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother appeals the juvenile court's decision denying her petition seeking to terminate the father's parental rights. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED. REMANDED.
